short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Convert coordinates between North East Down, Earth Centered Earth Fixed, SVY21, GDM, MGRS, UTM, Borneo RSO, WGS84, EPSG etc.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This web app can be used for converting geo-coordinate points between North East Down (local coordinate system NED), Earth Centered Earth Fixed (ECEF), SVY21, GDM, MGRS, UTM, Borneo RSO,  and WGS84 geo-latitude and longitude, and many other EPSG coordinate systems.
